===Noun===
;pivot
A '''pivot''' is that on which something turns; specifically a [[metal]] [[point]]ed [[pin]] or short [[shaft]] in [[machinery]], such as the end of an [[axle]] or [[spindle]].

It has specific technical meanings in [[linguistics]] and [[mathematics]].
{{wikipedia}}

===Verb===
;pivot
#to turn on an exact spot

===Etymology===
From [[French language|French]] ''pivot'', probably connected with [[Italian language|Italian]] ''pivolo'', "peg, pin", diminutive of ''piva'', ''pipa'', "pipe").